      label="Client Platform Feature"
      version="1.0.0"
      provider-name="University of Oldenburg">

   <description>
      This feature bundles the platform for the client product. So,
it defines the container where Odysseus is running in.
This includes for example Equinox and RCP.
Therefore, it does not provide any functionality by itself and
has no dependency to the core or other features.
   </description>

